data.description: Welcome home! This newer, spacious 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem sits on a generous half-acre lot in the desirable TK School District. The main floor boasts an open concept with beautiful wood flooring and a cozy gas log fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms and two bathrooms, including an owner's suite with a double vanity and a huge walk-in closet. Need more space? The finished basement offers a fantastic recreation room and is roughed in for an additional full bath. Outside, you'll enjoy the convenience of underground irrigation, a third stall garage, and two large private decks. Call for a private showing today! - Listing agent related to seller.
